But the tangential drift makes a system wise.

21:25.740 --> 21:29.700
Because a wise configuration isn't merely one that fits the data perfectly.

21:29.940 --> 21:30.260
Right.

21:30.260 --> 21:37.020
It is one that resides in a flat, expansive, low-curvature region of the RSVP space.

