It is not because the flat valley represents the absolute lowest possible energy state.

22:15.340 --> 22:15.600
Right.

22:15.600 --> 22:18.580
The perfect, ultimate, singular answer.

22:18.780 --> 22:19.040
Right.

22:19.600 --> 22:23.640
It finds the flat valley simply because of tangential entropy.

22:24.300 --> 22:25.100
The wiggle room.

22:25.300 --> 22:25.680
Exactly.

22:26.200 --> 22:26.880
The wiggle room.

22:27.560 --> 22:32.960
The flat regions physically occupy the most volume in the high-dimensional space.

22:33.180 --> 22:33.840
Oh, I see.

