22:58.920 --> 23:01.700
the basin takes up so much spatial volume.

23:01.860 --> 23:02.420
Wow.

23:02.420 --> 23:07.100
So we are basically wandering blindfolded through a room of truth.

23:07.660 --> 23:10.680
Everything in this high-dimensional room is technically factual.

23:11.360 --> 23:13.520
We aren't looking for a needle in a haystack.

23:13.780 --> 23:19.340
We are just trying to find the fluffiest, widest, most forgiving couch in the room to sit down

23:19.340 --> 23:19.620
on.

23:19.760 --> 23:21.140
The biggest volume of comfort.

23:21.600 --> 23:21.900
Right.

23:22.300 --> 23:27.500
We settle there not because it's mathematically perfect, but because it's the easiest place

23:27.500 --> 23:30.740
to stay stable despite all the noise of the world.

23:30.740 --> 23:34.200
You are seeking the highest tangential entropy.

23:35.420 --> 23:41.560
A stable worldview is one that remains true across the widest range of possible tangential

23:41.560 --> 23:42.400
interpretations.

23:42.840 --> 23:48.080
Okay, but this sets up a massive theoretical collision, doesn't it?

23:48.420 --> 23:49.640
Where are you going with this?

