The three signatures are a persistent action floor, tangent instability, and non-convergence

36:04.000 --> 36:05.660
of stochastic trajectories.

36:05.840 --> 36:07.940
We need to look at each of these closely.

36:08.360 --> 36:10.760
Let's start with a persistent action floor.

36:11.000 --> 36:14.360
Action, meaning the energy or movement of the system.

